mall village\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"the southeastern coast\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1096}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And while it would have made sense to keep the games strictly in France, Teahupo'o ultimately won the bid thanks to widespread support from its surfing community.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1191, \"end\": 1197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9990910138343764, \"rank\": 0.0008966613347307087, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sense\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1160}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1178}, {\"ngram\": \"Teahupo'o\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1208}, {\"ngram\": \"the bid thanks\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1238}, {\"ngram\": \"widespread support\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"its surfing community\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was also reportedly selected due to a lack of waves across Europe in the summertime, with International Surfing Association (ISA) President, Fernando Aguerre, explaining toTYC Sports: \\\"It was not easy, it has been a long time, but the IOC [International Olympic Committee] understood that in these weeks, in France, there was a great chance that there would be no waves and that the change would not only allow us to continue in France but also go to the best course where a tournament of this importance could be held.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1383, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Surfing Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1533, \"end\": 1564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1601, \"end\": 1607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9990910138343764, \"rank\": 0.0008966613347307087, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1722, \"end\": 1728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9990910138343764, \"rank\": 0.0008966613347307087, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lack\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1335}, {\"ngram\": \"waves\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1344}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"the summertime\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1376}, {\"ngram\": \"(ISA) President\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1432}, {\"ngram\": \"Fernando Aguerre\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1450}, {\"ngram\": \"Sports\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"the IOC\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1531}, {\"ngram\": \"these weeks\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"a great chance\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1633}, {\"ngram\": \"no waves\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1662}, {\"ngram\": \"the change\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1682}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1706}, {\"ngram\": \"the best course\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1759}, {\"ngram\": \"a tournament\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"this importance\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It really will be a dream come true.\\\"\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1850, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a dream\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking of the prestige of the waves in Teahupo'o, Aguerre said: \\\"It has a coral reef, one and a half metres below the water, in the shape of a ring, where impressive tubes are produced.\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 2039, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the prestige\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1876}, {\"ngram\": \"the waves\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1889}, {\"ngram\": \"Teahupo'o\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1902}, {\"ngram\": \"Aguerre\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"a coral reef\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 1938}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"the shape\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1991}, {\"ngram\": \"a ring\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2001}, {\"ngram\": \"impressive tubes\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike other breaks, where surfers go down the wave and then perform different manoeuvres for 10/15 seconds to get the best scores, in Teahupo'o it is something else, faster and more radical.\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2231, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other breaks\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2059}, {\"ngram\": \"surfers\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2074}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"different manoeuvres\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"10/15 seconds\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2147}, {\"ngram\": \"the best scores\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"Teahupo'o\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2184}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2277, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Discovery+is\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2247}, {\"ngram\": \"the new home\", \"from\": 2248