r\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2558}, {\"ngram\": \"the tube\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2590}, {\"ngram\": \"the foam ball\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2657}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The size of the wave is measured, how difficult the descent is, how deep you were in the tube and the time you stayed inside.\\\"\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2822, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The size\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2704}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"the descent\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2755}, {\"ngram\": \"the tube\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 2789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2933, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your sign-up\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2843}, {\"ngram\": \"content\", \"from\": 2855, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2870}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 3010, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"adverts\", \"from\": 2951, \"to\": 2958}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2966}, {\"ngram\": \"3rd parties\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 2982}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 3011, \"to\": 3043, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 3034, \"to\": 3042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy He added: \\\"It is one of the most complex waves in the world and in this tournament there will be the best surfers on the planet, 24 women and 24 men, from 21 countries and five continents.\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3066}, {\"ngram\": \"the most complex waves\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3113}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3117, \"to\": 3126}, {\"ngram\": \"this tournament\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3149}, {\"ngram\": \"the best surfers\", \"from\": 3164, \"to\": 3180}, {\"ngram\": \"the planet\", \"from\": 3184, \"to\": 3194}, {\"ngram\": \"24 women\", \"from\": 3196, \"to\": 3204}, {\"ngram\": \"24 men\", \"from\": 3209, \"to\": 3215}, {\"ngram\": \"21 countries\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3234}, {\"ngram\": \"five continents\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3254}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We expect tremendous competition, in the best possible place.\\\"\", \"from\": 3257, \"to\": 3319, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tremendous competition\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3289}, {\"ngram\": \"the best possible place\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not the first time that an Olympic Games has been split across two continents either.\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3411, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 3330, \"to\": 3344}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3350, \"to\": 3366}, {\"ngram\": \"two continents\", \"from\": 3389, \"to\": 3403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 1956 Summer Olympic Games were held in Melbourne, Australia, but due to strict equine quarantining at the time, the equestrian events were held around 15,500km away in Stockholm, Sweden.\", \"from\": 3412, \"to\": 3602, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3455, \"end\": 3464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9999956407941198, \"rank\": 4.309763361193113e-06, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 3466, \"end\": 3475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999996651823145, \"rank\": 1.6143764198484588e-07,